             was indicted for <rs id="t18020714-43-off223" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18020714-43-off223" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18020714-43-off223" type="offenceSubcategory" value="grandLarceny"></interp>
               feloniously stealing, on the <rs id="t18020714-43-cd224" type="crimeDate">20th of June</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18020714-43-off223 t18020714-43-cd224"></join>, a petticoat, value 5s. two aprons, value 2s. a gown, value 5s. and a pair of stays, value 6s. the property of 
                     <persName id="t18020714-43-victim466" type="victimName">
                        Mary 
                        Yates
                     <interp inst="t18020714-43-victim466" type="surname" value="Yates"></interp>
