                     <interp inst="t18020714-43-person474" type="gender" value="female"></interp>
                  </persName>
            .)</p>
               <p>
                  <xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="180207140033"></xptr>Prisoner's defence. I know nothing of it any more than a child unborn, these things I purchased for seven shillings and sixpence.</p>
               <p>
                  <rs id="t18020714-43-verdict229" type="verdictDescription">
